<html id="html-block-html" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/common--theme/base/css/html-block.css"/></head><body>
<script type="text/javascript">
today = new Date();
BigDay = new Date("January 1, 2022"); // 将此日期修改为你想倒计时的日期
msPerDay = 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000 ; // Vbs
timeLeft = (BigDay.getTime() - today.getTime());// Vbs
e_daysLeft = timeLeft / msPerDay;// Vbs
daysLeft = Math.floor(e_daysLeft);// Vbs
e_hrsLeft = (e_daysLeft - daysLeft)*24;// Vbs
hrsLeft = Math.floor(e_hrsLeft);// Vbs
minsLeft = Math.floor((e_hrsLeft - hrsLeft)*60);// Vbs
document.write("距离2022年仅有 " + daysLeft + " 天、" + hrsLeft +" 小时、" + minsLeft + " 分钟</H4>。<P>");
// 我基于一些我从moonfruit.com上找到的东西制作了这个，版权属于他们。
</script>
